<br>
Cleric pulls with stun, no damage low aggro, no call for help.<br>
<br>
Scout pulls with bow, does critical, big damage = big aggro<br>
<br>
Armsman pulls with crossbow, short range means taking some hits on the way back = healing induced aggro. <br>
<br>
Low or no damage spells are good to pull with since aggro is not a problem and range is good.  MOB's will not do their call for help thing as well. <br>
